I"<h2 id="pontifications">Pontifications</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/536914/change-agent-by-daniel-suarez/9781101984666/">Change Agent</a> is a terrible book aka <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2017/4/18/15162608/change-agent-daniel-suarez-movie-option-genetic-engineering-review">I agree with the Verge</a> but it is a frighteningly entertaining extrapolation of how <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CRISPR">CRISPR</a>-like technology could screw us.</li>
  <li>CRISPR-maggedon like previous armaggedons like nuclear winter, acid rain, global climate change-maggedon, etc  all are possible and we should try to prevent them but the real danger is conventional warfare started by the threat of one of these armaggedons.</li>
</ul>
